DESCRIPTION:Freakier FridayWhat better way to celebrate Friday the 13th tha
 n watching the follow-up to Freaky Friday\, the 2003 Lindsay Lohan and Jam
 ie Lee Curtis classic? Indeed\, more than 20 years have passed since mothe
 r and daughter switched bodies and literally lived the other’s life. It 
 turns out to be a family thing. This sequel has even more body swapping th
 an the original and you’ll love that they include a nod to Lindsay Lohan
 's The Parent Trap. Starring Jamie Lee Curtis\, Lindsay Lohan\, Julia But
 ters\, and Sophia Hammons. 2025 : 111 minutes : PG for thematic elements\
 , rude humor\, language and some suggestive references : ComedyWatch the t
 railer for Freakier Friday.Find Freakier Friday in the library catalog.
CATEGORIES:Movie
