CREATED:20251204T151206Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260126T190923Z
DESCRIPTION:Learn about the basics of personal finance\, budgeting\, and in
 troductory saving and investment strategies\, including factors in decidin
 g when\, where\, and how to save\, invest\, or tackle debt. Resources and 
 tools for learning more about these topics will be shared.Dr. Ryan Decker\
 , CFP is a Professor of Finance at North Central College where he serves a
 s the Founding Director of the Center for Financial Literacy. Dr. Decker r
 uns financial education programs for high schools\, colleges\, nonprofit o
 rganizations\, and corporations.This webinar is part of Financial Fitness 
 2026\, a free financial literacy series presented by BIG (Business Interes
 t Group)\, comprised of business librarians in the Chicago suburbs. These 
 virtual programs offer practical tips and advice from experienced financia
 l advisors.Register here to receive a Zoom link.Keyword: Consumer Informat
 ion
