DESCRIPTION:Violinist Alexandra Dreesen is a freshman at Adlai E. Stevenson
  High School. She studies violin with Injoo Choi and also plays viola. Ing
 rid is a merit scholarship student in the Music Institute of Chicago Acade
 my\, where she is also a member of Amerela Trio\, the youngest chamber ens
 emble of the Academy. She was awarded the prize for best interpretation of
