SUMMARY:Talking Tech: Streaming Services
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.skokielibrary.info/event/talking-tech-streaming-s
 ervices-16229
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20251204T213323Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20251229T192153Z
DESCRIPTION:Streaming services used to be an option to help "cut the cable 
 cord\," but now it seems like there are higher fees and bundling options t
 hat make the choices less clear-cut. And why does it always seem like what
  you want to watch is never on the platform you pay for? In this discussi
 on\, we'll explore the streaming entertainment options like Netflix\, Disn
 ey+\, Hulu\, and more. We'll look things up in real time and share our per
 sonal preferences about the best ways to tune in.
CATEGORIES:Technology
