BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:16130
DTSTAMP:20260311T170241Z
SUMMARY:Retirement Reality with Jill Schlesinger
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.skokielibrary.info/event/retirement-reality-jill-
 schlesinger-16130
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20251204T155841Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260302T222016Z
DESCRIPTION:Are you thinking about retirement? Does it seem completely out 
 of reach? CBS News Business Analyst Jill Schlesinger\, will walk through t
 he specific steps necessary to get you where you want to go\, whether you 
 are just starting off in your career or ready to wind down. Jill takes the
  mystery out of finances to help you take control of your own.Jill Schlesi
 nger\, CFP\, a winner of the Emmy Award and Gracie Award\, translates comp
 licated business and economic news into understandable\, relatable topics 
 for everyday viewers and listeners. She covers the economy\, markets\, inv
 esting and anything else with a dollar sign on TV\, podcasts\, and radio. 
 Jill also won a 2018 Personal Finance Reporting Award from the Radio Telev
 ision Digital News Association/National Endowment for Financial Education.
 This webinar is part of Financial Fitness 2026. Financial Fitness is a fre
 e financial literacy series presented by BIG (Business Interest Group)\, a
  group of business librarians in the Chicago suburbs. In support of the li
 braries’ mission of providing access to reliable information\, these vir
 tual programs offer practical tips and advice from experienced financial a
 dvisors.Register here to receive a Zoom link. After you register\, you wil
 l receive a confirmation email in the form of a calendar invite. If you ha
 ve any questions after you register\, please contact ILfinancialfitness@gm
 ail.com.
CATEGORIES:Self-Improvement
DTSTART:20260422T000000Z
