 ly\, to taking guitar classes at the Old Town School of Folk Music\, to em
 barking on a career that took him across the country learning and writing 
 new songs all the while. Accompanied by guitar\, 5-string banjo\, and 12-
 string guitar\, the program reflects on our common musical heritage.Free t
 ickets will be given to those present starting at 2:30 pm.
