UID:24242
DTSTAMP:20260311T170242Z
SUMMARY:Talking Books
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.skokielibrary.info/event/talking-books-24242
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260205T214202Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260304T173113Z
DESCRIPTION:This month we'll be discussing The Garden of Evening Mists by T
 an Twan Eng.Seeking solace in the Malaysian plantations of her childhood a
 fter grueling World War II experiences\, criminal prosecutor Yun Ling Teoh
  discovers a Japanese garden and its enigmatic tender\, an exiled Japanese
  royal gardener who reluctantly accepts her as an apprentice.All are welco
 me\, whether you read in print\, braille\, audio\, or simply want to join 
