UID:23920
DTSTAMP:20260311T170242Z
SUMMARY:Friday Film
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.skokielibrary.info/event/friday-film-23920
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260204T005713Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260304T173204Z
DESCRIPTION:A Nice Indian BoyNaveen\, a successful doctor\, has always drea
 med of having a Bollywood-style wedding like his sister’s. His guarded n
 ature\, however\, has kept him from finding Mr. Right. Enter Jay: a white 
 freelance photographer who was adopted by an Indian couple\, speaks Hindi\
 , and prays to Ganesha. They share a lot in common and quickly fall in lov
 e. But as Naveen introduces Jay to his traditional parents\, they must fac
 e the ‘bigness of love’ and complexities of family and marriage.Starri
 ng Harish Patel\, Jonathan Groff\, Karan Soni\, Peter S. Kim\, Sunita Mani
 \, and Zarna Garg. Directed by Roshan Sethi.2024 : 96 minutes : Not rated 
 : Romantic comedyFree tickets will be given to those who attend.Watch a tr
 ailer for A Nice Indian Boy.Find A Nice Indian Boy in the library catalog.
CATEGORIES:Movie
