 movie-23898
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260203T223407Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260304T201236Z
DESCRIPTION:Strange WorldThis screening is designed for everyone\, includin
 g families with neurodivergent children and others who may benefit from a 
 less sensory-intense movie experience. We will keep the lights on and turn
  the sound down so you can shout\, sing\, or move about however you need t
 o enjoy the film.In Strange World\, a family of explorers deal with family
  conflicts while also adventuring into uncharted lands.2022 : 102 minutes 
 : Rated PG for action/peril and some thematic elements : Animation\, Adven
 ture\, Sci-FiFree tickets will be given to all who attend. Children younge
 r than eight must be accompanied by an adult.Watch the trailer for Strange
  World.Find Strange World in the library catalog.
